						<h3>The very first Random Chimp Event</h3>
						<p>This Random Chimp Event took place on 19-1-2009. Because the government was so unprofessional when covering up the mess the Chimps made, we were able to gather many details.</p>
						<p>At 11:00 exactly, a sole Chimp entered the Marcy Projects hallway, exiting a few minutes later carrying multiple bags which carried stolen valuables, including cash, jewellery and even TV cameras. When we asked the many eyewitnesses inside what happened, all of them had the same story, depicted below (ACTUAL TESTIMONY):<br><br>"So we were enjoying the 2009 World Series of Dice and things were actually going good, no robberies, everyone was happy, when this weird chimp came in, started to shoot at the ceiling and yelling like all them apes do. It stole everything we had, cash, rings, even the producers cameras. It even shot one of the contestants for their money! Damn!" 
						</p>
